{"type": "article", "id": 4374, "title": "Moleskine iPhone 保护套", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-15T07:55:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606004148463SjpBd7g1tR9ai.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t用惯了 Moleskine 笔记本的朋友总能说出无数个喜爱它的理由呢，那如果是一款酷似 Moleskine 笔记本的手机保护套呢？日前，Moleskine 就专门为 iPhone 6 设计了一款手机保护套，外形照搬了经典的 Moleskine 笔记本的样式，就连使用方式也都与笔记本一样设计为了开合式。除了为手机提供保护功能之外，这款保护套还兼有卡包的功能，可以收纳日常所用的银行卡等小物件。据悉，这款保护套将于本月底上市。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004145aR36GdEj9nqmYDke.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004146JtsvSgnUXmbKZQR1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004146WcK3g6XID8qF0MZt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.34375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004147UxOLFX2haq0w648d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.41875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}